86
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:11,790
you are trying to create a new entity.

87
00:05:11,790 --> 00:05:13,390
If you do not want that

88
00:05:14,529 --> 00:05:16,140
then you should never populate a navigation

89
00:05:16,140 --> 00:05:19,740
property when you are trying to insert a record

90
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:23,673
in Entity Framework Core, always remember that.

91
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:28,050
So work around to this particular issue is we

92
00:05:28,050 --> 00:05:33,050
can have a new application user, call that application user,

