00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,270
So that is one thing that you should always

96
00:05:45,615 --> 00:05:48,171
remember when you see that Entity Framework Core

97
00:05:48,171 --> 00:05:50,133
is trying to add a navigation property,

98
00:05:51,568 --> 00:05:54,750
